        .container 
          .column
            .content 
              .logo 
                img(src="./assets/images/logo-shopley-color.png", alt="")
              p.description Shopley is an interactive, mobile commerce platform (mPOS) focused on Hospitality and Retail.  We turn every cell phone into a personal shopping cart to create a fully interactive store enhancing communication between staff and consumers, for co-shopping, collecting real-time data and turning it into personalized insights which can be used to retarget customers after checkout, through the platform.
